'''Stinkweed''' was a type of [[Plant/Legends|plant]] found on [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]].<ref name="SOTEPG">''[[Shadows of the Empire Planets Guide]]''</ref> The term could also be used as an insult.<ref name="Life Below">{{CWACite|9|Life Below}}</ref>

Stinkweed could confused even the [[krak'jya]]'s keen sense of smell, and [[hunting/Legends|hunters]] sometimes camouflaged by hiding in it.<ref name="SOTEPG" />

